<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">צוּד</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
צוּד / tsûd / tsood

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''צוּד'''

# To lie alongside (that is, in wait); by implication to catch an animal (figuratively men); (denominative from {{HH|6718}}) to [[victual]] (for a journey): - [[chase]], [[hunt]], [[sore]], take (provision).

